subpanels.description: Front view of hemi-maxillary from Prémontré (Paris Basin, MP 10), showing the large infraorbitary foramen of SLP29PR-1312, stored in the Montpellier University collections (ISE-M), Hartenbergeromys hautefeuillei. Scale bar 1 mm.
Front view of hemi-maxillary from Prémontré (Paris Basin, MP 10), showing the large infraorbitary foramen of SLP29PR-960, Pantrogna marandati. Scale bar 1 mm.
